# National-Blood-Radar
National Blood Radar â€“ Zero Waste Network
A real-time AI-enhanced monitoring system 
that tracks blood inventory levels across 
all regions and hospitals,
generating a dynamic Blood Risk Score based on shortages,
expiry risk, and demand pressure.
The platform includes interactive what-if analysis, 
smart transfer optimization, and AI-driven insights to prevent stockouts, 
reduce waste, and support rapid decision-making on a national scale.
